page.title: 11HOME LIFE
page.content: {10.15}We get on the bus. {10.20}We arrive at swimming pool. {10.35}We have our swimming lesson. {11.15}We get out of the pool and dress {11.30}Leave changing room for the bus. {11.50}We arrive back at school. {11.55}We wash hands for lunch. {12.00}We say Grace. {12.03}We eat our lunch. {12.20}I finish lunch and go to play. {1.00}We come back into class. {1.05}Mrs.Smith takes us for science. {2.00}We go out to play. {2.15}Come in and start reading. {3.15}It's the end of school.We go outside,and get in the car. {3.25}We arrive home.I put my bags on the floor. {3.27}I go upstairs and get changed. {3.35}I have a Chewy Bar.
